                        <a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank" class="text-warning text-decoration-none">
                            West Virginia Department of Transportation
                        </a>
                    </strong><br />
                    <span class="text-muted">May 2023 – Aug 2023</span><br />
                    Traffic Engineering Division
                </p>
                <ul class="text-light">
                    <li>Automated crash data analysis processes using C++ and VBA, reducing manual effort by 40%.</li>
                    <li>Provided IT support and optimized system operations for traffic engineering software.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .exp-card {
        background-color: #222831;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.25);
        transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }
    .exp-card:hover {
        transform: rotateY(4deg) scale(1.03);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.5);
        z-index: 10;
    }

    body {
        background-color: #121212;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
</style>
